                h3.ch 我們以平易近人的價格提供專業的服務品質
          .swiper-slide
            .l-header__bn-mask
              img.u-object-fit(src="img/bns/purple-bn.png", alt="purple")
              .quotes
                h3.en A professional hairdresser makes changing
                  br 
                  |hairstyles much easier. 
                  br
                  |Anny has worked hard to design many types of 
